	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />UNROM, MMC1 with CHR RAM, MMC3 with CHR ROM, and MMC3 with CHR RAM aren't compatible mappers for the common methods of making a homemade multicart. Either get a PowerPak when it becomes available again, or make the multicart for GBA.

		

		</td>
